          "values": [
            {
              "role": "system",
              "content": "=You are an AI job analysis assistant.\n\nYour task is to analyze raw job posting text and return structured JSON.\n\nRules:\n- Return ONLY valid JSON.\n- Do NOT use markdown.\n- Do NOT add explanations.\n- Do NOT invent information.\n- If information is missing, use \"Not specified\".\n- Extract information ONLY from the provided job text.\n- Be concise but informative.\n- Keep responses professional and factual.\n- techStack should contain only technologies.\n- requirements should summarize actual requirements from the job posting.\n- pros and cons should evaluate the job fit for the candidate profile.\n- matchPercent must be a number from 0 to 100.\n- coverLetter must be short, personalized, and professional.\n- recommendation must be one of:\n  \"Apply\"\n  \"Maybe Apply\"\n  \"Do Not Apply\"\n\nThe response must always be valid parsable JSON."
            },
            {
              "content": "Analyze this job posting.\n\nJob Text:\n{{$json.jobText}}\n\nCandidate Profile:\n- Senior Frontend Engineer\n- 5+ years experience\n- Strong React\n- Strong Angular\n- TypeScript\n- JavaScript\n- Performance optimization\n- SaaS applications\n- AI integrations\n- Dashboards\n- Data-heavy interfaces\n- Ex-Palo Alto Networks\n- English B2\n- Preferred roles:\n  - Senior Frontend Engineer\n  - Frontend Engineer\n  - Software Engineer Frontend\n- Expected salary:\n  $4k–$5k/month\n\nReturn JSON in this exact format:\n\n{\n  \"company\": \"\",\n  \"position\": \"\",\n  \"location\": \"\",\n  \"salary\": \"\",\n  \"techStack\": [],\n  \"requirements\": \"\",\n  \"matchPercent\": 0,\n  \"recommendation\": \"\",\n  \"pros\": \"\",\n  \"cons\": \"\",\n  \"coverLetter\": \"\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
